value.ProgramElementNote.record: Note: FY 2013 Previous President's Budget (FY 2014) amount shown in B. Program Change Summary is an electronic error and should be $10073.
value.ProgramElementMissionDescription.r: This program element supports component development and prototyping for organizational equipment improved individual clothing and equipment that enhance Soldier battlefield effectiveness survivability and sustainment.  This program element also supports the component development and prototyping of joint service food and combat feeding equipment designed to reduce logistics burden.
